      <title>韩国警告朝鲜边境有寄生虫，朝鲜向边境投放更多垃圾气球</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/north-korea-sends-more-trash-balloons-over-border-as-south-warns-of-parasites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国政府称，在朝鲜之前的垃圾气球中检测到蛔虫等寄生虫后，朝鲜又向韩国境内派出了一批携带垃圾的气球。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/north-korea-sends-more-trash-balloons-over-border-as-south-warns-of-parasites</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 01:52:50 GMT</pubDate>
