    <item>
      <title>日本母子在上海附近城市遭持刀袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/japanese-mother-child-attacked-with-knife-in-city-near-shanghai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名日本妇女和她的孩子在中国上海附近的一个城市遭到持刀袭击，这让这个暴力事件罕见的国家出现了一系列持刀伤人事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/japanese-mother-child-attacked-with-knife-in-city-near-shanghai</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 01:41:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平呼吁中国在与美国的芯片之战中打击竞争对手的技术主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/xi-urges-china-to-combat-rivals-tech-dominance-amid-chip-battle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平呼吁中国加强创新，因为其他国家在某些关键技术上占据主导地位，这一言论凸显了中国与美国在半导体领域的对抗不断升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/xi-urges-china-to-combat-rivals-tech-dominance-amid-chip-battle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 01:19:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
